review_blob: Ver nice and clear pilsner. Aroma is good but not strong. Head is not strong. Colour yellowy, chryctally clear. Taste is very good and fresh with medium sweetness and light soury,salty. Body is creamy, not light, medium carbonization. Finish with flower aroma. Very nice beer for every day, but nothing special.
